      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "A **relation** from $A$ to $B$ is a subset of $A \\times B$.",
        "Properties: **reflexive**, **symmetric**, \n **antisymmetric**, **transitive**.",
        "**Equivalence relation**: reflexive, symmetric, transitive.",
        "**Equivalence class** $[a]$: all elements equivalent to $a$.",
        "Equivalence relations correspond bijectively to **partitions**.",
        "**Partial order**: reflexive, antisymmetric, transitive.",
        "**Total order**: a partial order where all elements are \n comparable.",
        "**Hasse diagram**: visual representation of a finite poset."
      ]
