      "text": "Review Exercises"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Determine which properties $R = \\{(1,1), (1,2), (2,1), (2,2), \n(3,3)\\}$ on $\\{1, 2, 3\\}$ has."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Is \"$a^2 = b^2$\" on $\\Z$ an equivalence relation? If so, \ndescribe the equivalence classes."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Show that \"$|a - b| \\leq 1$\" on $\\Z$ is reflexive and symmetric \nbut not transitive."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Draw the Hasse diagram for $(\\{1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 8, 12, 24\\}, \\mid)$."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "How many distinct equivalence relations are there on a 4-element \nset?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In the poset $(\\mathcal{P}(\\{a, b, c\\}), \\subseteq)$, find the \ngreatest and least elements."
